WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.230
Amen. He said there's going to be a new

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:04.670
wave of patriotism coming out, and that's

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:07.309
whenever I saw Trump and

00:00:07.319 --> 00:00:11.110
a red wave coming out of Michigan.

00:00:11.120 --> 00:00:12.910
Then I saw Oklahoma, and there

00:00:12.910 --> 00:00:12.920
were

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:15.669
embers of people, and they all

00:00:15.679 --> 00:00:17.630
had torches

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:18.830
throughout Oklahoma. They were

00:00:18.840 --> 00:00:20.509
raising up these torches that looked

00:00:20.519 --> 00:00:22.830
like fire, and they were bringing forth a

00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:25.750
new patriotism upon the nation.

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:27.390
It was being birthed and it

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.509
just kept spreading like fire all

00:00:29.519 --> 00:00:31.070
throughout America. I

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:33.869
saw Trump rising up, and then I saw an

00:00:33.879 --> 00:00:37.110
attempt on his life: this bullet

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:40.549
flew by his ear and it came so close to

00:00:40.559 --> 00:00:43.510
his head that it busted his eardrum.

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:46.590
He fell to his knees

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:48.869
during this timeframe and he started

00:00:48.879 --> 00:00:50.990
worshiping the Lord. He got radically

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.549
born again during this

00:00:53.549 --> 00:00:53.559
timeframe—I'm

00:00:53.559 --> 00:00:56.189
talking, people say he's saved now, but he

00:00:56.199 --> 00:00:59.470
becomes really on fire for Jesus

00:00:59.470 --> 00:00:59.480
from

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:02.150
what I saw coming. Then I saw

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:04.990
people interceding,

00:01:04.990 --> 00:01:05.000
and

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:07.990
I saw him winning the presidency. The

00:01:07.990 --> 00:01:08.000
Lord showed

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.149
me it

00:01:10.159 --> 00:01:12.109
would go clear into the summer; great

00:01:12.119 --> 00:01:14.109
persecution would come on him through

00:01:14.119 --> 00:01:16.590
the judges and through the

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.270
law and all these people trying to

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:19.830
sue him, but there

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:21.710
would be a stop to it and things

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:23.950
would start to break free

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:25.830
toward the fall. Then I saw him

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:28.749
winning the election through

00:01:28.759 --> 00:01:30.510
the patriots coming out and

00:01:30.510 --> 00:01:30.520
voting.

00:01:30.520 --> 00:01:32.030
Then there will be

00:01:32.040 --> 00:01:34.990
a great economic crash. I saw they had a

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:38.550
great economic plan, a crash worse than

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.950
the Great Depression. The Lord

00:01:40.960 --> 00:01:43.149
warned me about this; it would be a great

00:01:43.159 --> 00:01:46.429
dark time, but I saw paddles coming upon

00:01:46.439 --> 00:01:48.950
America's soil like a shocking of the

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:51.990
soil. I saw Donald Trump praying in

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.630
the Oval Office and

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:56.910
he was weeping before the Lord with his

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:58.429
hands on his head. There

00:01:58.429 --> 00:01:58.439
were

00:01:58.439 --> 00:02:00.950
ministers and

00:02:00.950 --> 00:02:00.960
people—I

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:01.990
don't know if they were

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.190
senators or

00:02:04.190 --> 00:02:04.200
congresspeople—I

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:06.990
just saw them pacing

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:09.990
back and forth inside of the

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.750
White House,

00:02:12.760 --> 00:02:14.270
the Oval

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:16.309
Office, and they were interceding all

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:17.790
inside there. I could feel the

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:19.509
presence of the Lord so strong on this.

00:02:19.519 --> 00:02:21.390
Then I could see that darkness,

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:24.110
the heaviness upon America with the

00:02:24.120 --> 00:02:28.270
financial crisis I

00:02:28.270 --> 00:02:28.280
saw coming,

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:30.430
started to

00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:33.030
lift above the trees and I saw the blue

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:34.710
and the

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:36.869
green times—good

00:02:36.869 --> 00:02:36.879
times—coming

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:38.630
back again. But the Lord said it

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:42.110
would be a season of

00:02:42.120 --> 00:02:44.750
a shaking, and it would be a

00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:44.760
shaking.

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:49.110
In this,

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:50.869
basically, he was not done with

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:52.710
America; there would be a great revival.

00:02:52.720 --> 00:02:54.630
It's not all doom

00:02:54.640 --> 00:02:56.070
and gloom; that's what he said. 'The sky is

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:58.910
not falling. It's just a

00:02:58.910 --> 00:02:58.920
time—people

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:00.030
would say this is judgment,'and the

00:03:00.030 --> 00:03:00.040
Lord said, 'Do

00:03:00.040 --> 00:03:01.869
not call

00:03:01.879 --> 00:03:03.789
this judgment. It's not my judgment; it's

00:03:03.799 --> 00:03:08.360
a correction. There's a correction coming.

